data.description:
Sitting on a corner lot in Big Rapids this home is ready for it's new owner. 
The yard is large but the best part is it is fenced in! Totally perfect for pets or children to be safe while enjoying the sunshine. Inside you will find a nice layout that offers 3 (possibly 4) bedrooms and a good sized bathroom. There is also a good sized 2 stall detached garage for parking. Make sure to schedule your showing today before it is sold.
